# 🎨 Project Assets

This directory holds the visual evidence of the Foundry applications developed during the sprint. Since the live sandbox cannot be shared publicly, these assets serve as visual proof-of-work.

## 🖼️ Included Media
* **Architecture Diagrams:** Visual flows mapping raw data sources to the target Ontology.
* **Pipeline Builder Graphs:** Visual data lineage and transform flows.
* **Workshop Apps:** Screenshots of the completed front-end applications, dashboards, and Action buttons.
